               <p>Q. to the Prosecutor. Are you sure your door was fast?</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. Yes.</p>
               <p>"The prisoner in his defence said, that he went up stairs to enquire for one Matthews, a shoe maker; going down stairs he knocked at the prosecutor's door, which flew open."</p>
               <p>He called 
               <persName id="t17710911-51-person531">
                  Jane
                   Lister
               <interp inst="t17710911-51-person531" type="surname" value="Lister"></interp>
