                     <interp inst="t17710911-51-person531" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , who said she went into the apartments of the prosecutor, at the time the prisoner was taken into custody; and that she heard the prosecutor say she did not lock the door herself, but that the lodgers did in the morning; she also said she was not acquainted with the prisoner.</p>
